1
00:01:06,239 --> 00:01:07,200
Mother

2
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:09,560
Will Father come again tonight?

3
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,640
Sweetheart

4
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:26,799
He won't be coming

5
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,040
Mother

6
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,560
I'm so scared

7
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:36,719
Drink this cup of wine

8
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,840
and you won't be afraid anymore

9
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:54,480
He won't be coming

10
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:59,120
Liu Heng

11
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,239
You dare show up here?

12
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:03,280
What now?

13
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,640
Loving the chaos, aren't you

14
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,799
Bite me if you've got the guts

15
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,000
No rush

16
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,840
I'll deal with you sooner or later

17
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,439
Wait

18
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,800
The Masked Wine God

19
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,560
Heh heh heh

20
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,400
Oh my

21
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:16,919
You actually tracked us all the way here

22
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,120
You really won't give up, will you

23
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:19,879
Hmph

24
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,960
Better lucky than early

25
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:24,080
Today, I'm going to take down

26
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,840
all of you at once

27
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,479
Come on

28
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:27,360
Brothers

29
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,400
Drink them under the table

30
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:29,800
Ten Men Crew, take down the Wine God

31
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:31,800
Whoa

32
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,240
Quite the lively gathering

33
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:37,560
Number Seven

34
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:40,000
I finally found you

35
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,400
I've been waiting for you too

36
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,240
Today, we're settling this once and for all

37
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:50,240
Good

38
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,000
Let's go

39
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,159
Move

40
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:53,520
Hey

41
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,639
Stop right there

42
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:58,120
Daring to ignore the Ten Men Crew

43
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,439
What's so impressive about a bunch of lackeys?

44
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:02,840
Hmph

45
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,800
If you don't beat us today,

46
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,360
none of you are leaving

47
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,639
Ugh

48
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:09,599
So annoying

49
00:03:10,919 --> 00:03:11,800
For fairness' sake

50
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,039
five each

51
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,240
Make it quick

52
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,319
Suits me just fine

53
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,520
Fine, you guys are tough

54
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,120
Trying to run?

55
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:25,759
You reap what you sow

56
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:26,240
Hey

57
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,120
Don't blame your big brother for not saving you

58
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:29,240
Forget it, forget it

59
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,919
Come on

60
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,560
Finally, just the two of us

61
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,759
Come on

62
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:44,919
Come

63
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,599
Lie'er

64
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,960
Lie'er, don't be hasty

65
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,759
Uncle Wang

66
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:06,080
I...

67
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,280
I...

68
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:11,120
I always thought you were just a dream of mine

69
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,719
It's my fault too

70
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:14,800
After you grew up

71
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:16,920
I had no choice but to leave the capital

72
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,439
The capital...

73
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:19,800
Uncle Wang

74
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:23,000
You're Wang Lie, the exiled Chief Guard.

75
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:28,040
Your servant greets the Crown Prince

76
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,120
If I've offended you before

77
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,600
Please forgive me

78
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:33,040
Uncle Wang

79
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,000
So you were actually exiled from the palace

80
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,839
Ah

81
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,439
If you hadn't left back then

82
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,639
I probably wouldn't be like this now

83
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,800
Who knows

84
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,040
Maybe you'd have truly become

85
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,399
a real human keg

86
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,000
Uncle Wang

87
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,759
Today we don't stop till we're drunk

88
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,160
All right

89
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:58,439
Come on

90
00:04:58,439 --> 00:04:59,160
Come on

91
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,800
Crown Prince

92
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:06,519
Something from 15 years ago

93
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:07,639
and you still remember it?

94
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,720
Not really

95
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:11,160
Guard Wang was deeply trusted by my late father

96
00:05:11,399 --> 00:05:12,959
So when he was exiled from the palace

97
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,040
it caused quite a stir across the city

98
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,240
Since the late Emperor trusted him so deeply

99
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,519
how did he end up exiled?

100
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:21,120
Ah

101
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,639
I don't know either

102
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,600
Father never told me the reason

103
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:31,800
Refreshing!

104
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,639
Great wine!

105
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:34,439
Great wine

106
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,639
Come on

107
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:40,160
No sleeping!

108
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:43,040
Hey

109
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,160
Ouyang Yan

110
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:45,519
You won't let me go

111
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,800
Fine, you won't feed me

112
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,120
And now you won't even let me sleep?

113
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,800
How can there be such a vicious woman?

114
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,920
When I'm Emperor, I won't marry you!

115
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:59,600
You're daydreaming, aren't you?

116
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,600
Becoming Emperor?

117
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:02,639
No, wait

118
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:05,040
I should become Emperor and marry you

119
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,439
Then take my revenge on you

120
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:08,839
As if you could ever become Emperor

121
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:09,360
Hey

122
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:09,800
Exactly

123
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,240
Too much!

124
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,519
Are you all right?

125
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,560
Don't

126
00:06:33,759 --> 00:06:34,560
Lie'er

127
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:36,839
I'm old now

128
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:38,800
Can't drink like I used to

129
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:40,600
You win today

130
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,439
No

131
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:43,000
You let me win

132
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,600
Uncle Wang, you let me win

133
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:46,160
Since you've already won

134
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:48,399
can you come back to the capital and be emperor?

135
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:49,319
No

136
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,120
No way

137
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,639
Why not?

138
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,519
I've changed my mind

139
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:57,439
I'm not making you the heir anymore

140
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,800
A drunkard as emperor?

141
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,800
That's outrageous

142
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,199
What did you say?

143
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,600
What's wrong with you?

144
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,120
So I did all this for nothing?

145
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:08,439
Well, thanks a lot

146
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,040
Being emperor

147
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:12,800
doesn't interest me at all

148
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:16,199
Now that I've met Uncle Wang

149
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,519
I'd rather stay with Uncle Wang

150
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:21,319
and guard this Lone Goblet City together

151
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:23,199
Oh, no

152
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:24,560
Fine, then

153
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,839
I won't interrupt your reunion

154
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,720
I'll take my leave

155
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:28,639
Don't bother seeing me out

156
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,560
What's gotten into him?

157
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,959
Actually, Chicken Boy has a point

158
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,199
Just look at him

159
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,439
Does he look like emperor material?

160
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,040
Let's go

161
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,240
Hey

162
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:48,839
You guys

163
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,040
Let me down, please

164
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:54,360
Don't worry

165
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,319
The winery staff will clear up tonight

166
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,439
Hey, wait for me

167
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,240
I still don't get it

168
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:06,199
Why did you change your mind so suddenly?

169
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:06,759
Oh, come on

170
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,360
Because they're not uncle and nephew

171
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,360
They're father and son

172
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:12,240
What?

173
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:15,319
I saw it in Wang Lie's memories

174
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,519
They really are father and son

175
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,639
Could it be...

176
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:20,199
that's why the late emperor banished him?

177
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,120
Exactly

178
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,959
Looking at it this way

179
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,360
Father was actually quite merciful

180
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,000
So he's not a prince after all

181
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,200
No wonder you suddenly dropped him

182
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,000
Not only that

183
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,200
They've only just been reunited

184
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,440
I can't bear to tear them apart

185
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:42,960
Hey

186
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,159
So in that case

187
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,240
Liu Lie's surname is Wang

188
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,440
Then he shares his father's name?

189
00:08:49,039 --> 00:08:50,399
Liu Lie must be Wang Lie's son

190
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,559
So he should be called Wang Lie

191
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,639
Wang Lie fathered Liu Lie

192
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,240
Liu Lie doesn't know he should be Wang Lie

193
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:54,799
Anyway

194
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,919
Whatever's between father and son

195
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,360
let them sort it out themselves

196
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,039
Let's go

197
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:04,360
What's wrong?

198
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:07,120
I'm fine

199
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:10,720
Just thinking how nice their reunion is.

200
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:14,200
It's really touching

201
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,519
Missing home, huh?

202
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:20,559
No way

203
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:22,759
Why drag me into this for no reason?

204
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,679
I'm leaving

205
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,240
Wait for me

206
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,320
No waiting, no waiting!

207
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,120
Fine, fine, fine, fine, fine.

208
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:39,840
Imperial Uncle Liu, following our plan,

209
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,919
has already invaded the Watanabe Kingdom.

210
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:43,799
Now that we've sent him away,

211
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:44,840
our next step

212
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,919
will be to...

213
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:46,840
Mm.

214
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,639
Excellent.

215
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:49,360
Imperial Uncle Liu is spread too thin.

216
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:53,240
Now's my perfect time to return to court.

217
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,159
But in the palace,

218
00:09:55,159 --> 00:09:56,759
General Li is still there.

219
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:58,120
It's fine, it's fine.

220
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:01,360
Once I meet up with Lord Song,

221
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,200
we'll plan our next move.

222
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,360
Your Eminence,

223
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:06,440
you're planning to enter the city?

224
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:07,840
Huh?

225
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:11,960
I don't think that's quite wise.

226
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:15,799
Why not?

227
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:17,159
Crown Prince,

228
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,440
do you still not trust me?

229
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:22,039
Your Eminence, how could you say that?

230
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:24,320
I just feel that going into the city now

231
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:26,120
is far too risky.

232
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,399
If you want to see Lord Song,

233
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:29,600
I'll send someone to fetch him.

234
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,360
Your Eminence,

235
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,840
safety comes first.

236
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,039
Right?

237
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,519
Mm.

238
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,759
Very well, then.

239
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:46,840
I'll have to trouble you, Crown Prince.

240
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:52,519
Crown Prince,

241
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,840
words alone won't suffice.

242
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:56,759
If you just tell him,

243
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:58,519
Lord Song won't believe you.

244
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,519
Take this with you,

245
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:03,440
and only then will Lord Song come along.

246
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:04,679
Oh.

247
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,440
Hold it carefully.

248
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:11,320
Hmph.

249
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,799
You really think of everything, Your Eminence.

250
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:16,000
I'll stay here and wait for you.

251
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:17,840
Ah.

252
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,440
Zhenzhen, you're not coming with us?

253
00:11:20,159 --> 00:11:22,159
I hear Prince Yu has many romantic exploits.

254
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:24,240
I plan to gather material in the city.

255
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:27,000
After all, gossip is always the juiciest.

256
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:27,519
Ah.

257
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:28,519
Hey.

258
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:32,519
Hey.

259
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:33,639
I've been thinking,

260
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:35,000
my status makes it awkward to meet Prince Yu.

261
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,200
Let's split up.

262
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,440
I'll leave Prince Yu to you two.

263
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:37,919
Good luck!

264
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:38,559
Hey.

265
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:40,440
Where are you going?

266
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,759
Need you ask?

267
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:43,960
Tomorrow.

268
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,240
Our Prince Yu retires early.

269
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,639
He sees no visitors after nightfall.

270
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,039
You two,

271
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:47,840
please leave.

272
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:49,200
Go announce us.

273
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:49,679
Just say

274
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:51,120
the Princess of Yan has come to see him.

275
00:11:52,799 --> 00:11:53,240
Hey.

276
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,120
Please go announce us.

277
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:57,039
Tell him we're envoys from the palace,

278
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,399
with an important matter to discuss.

279
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,919
If it's an important matter,

280
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,519
then all the more reason to wait till tomorrow.

281
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,039
Hey.

282
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:06,120
Why didn't you let me jump in just now?

283
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,840
Oh, come on.

284
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,639
We'll see him tomorrow.

285
00:12:07,639 --> 00:12:08,919
Why are you in such a hurry?

286
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,840
It's not that I want to see him.

287
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:13,159
No visitors after dark?

288
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,639
A woman's intuition tells me

289
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:16,799
something's not right here.

290
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,320
Oh?

291
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,440
And which woman told you that?

292
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:22,759
Hey.

293
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:25,039
Look, that person seems strange.

294
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:26,879
Hmm.

295
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:28,799
Let's follow and see.

296
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,200
I'm not going.

297
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,639
Boring.

298
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:34,039
Hey.

299
00:12:34,039 --> 00:12:34,919
Wait for me!

300
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,440
Our Prince Yu...

301
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,840
I'm not here to see your Prince Yu.

302
00:12:55,519 --> 00:12:56,639
Then who are you here for?

303
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,320
Forgive my poor hospitality yesterday.

304
00:12:58,639 --> 00:12:59,960
I hope the envoy and the princess

305
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,639
will not take it to heart.

306
00:13:02,519 --> 00:13:03,159
Ah.

307
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:03,960
This child...

308
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:06,720
He works hard all day long,

309
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:09,440
so he tends to sleep early at night.

310
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:10,759
It's no matter.

311
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:13,519
Now that the late emperor has passed,

312
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,360
Watanabe Kingdom watches us like a hawk.

313
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,720
The court is in turmoil.

314
00:13:17,799 --> 00:13:19,639
Since Prince Yu has the talent to govern,

315
00:13:19,639 --> 00:13:21,399
would he be willing to return with us

316
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:22,200
to ascend the throne?

317
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:24,200
Well...

318
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:26,360
Ah.

319
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,559
This child

320
00:13:27,559 --> 00:13:30,320
cares deeply for the people of Jade City.

321
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,840
He can't bear to leave.

322
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,240
Then let's hurry and leave.

323
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,799
Time is short and the task is great.

324
00:13:36,799 --> 00:13:38,159
Let's find the next candidate quickly.

325
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:41,120
Prince Yu is rare in his loyalty.

326
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:43,919
Your Highness.

327
00:13:43,919 --> 00:13:45,840
Regarding ascending the throne,

328
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,240
please think it over carefully.

329
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,200
Though I hate to leave my people,

330
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:55,399
I can't ignore the fate of Daliang either.

331
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:58,200
For the sake of Daliang's kingdom,

332
00:13:58,799 --> 00:14:00,360
I'm willing to return with you.

333
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,679
But once you're emperor, make me empress.

334
00:14:04,639 --> 00:14:06,000
I'm known to hit people, you know.

335
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,120
Think it through carefully.

336
00:14:09,159 --> 00:14:10,600
Watanabe grows more arrogant by the day.

337
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,799
Daliang and Yan should unite as one.

338
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,960
And besides,

339
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,879
being able to marry the princess

340
00:14:16,879 --> 00:14:18,639
is my honor.

341
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,960
Prince Yu truly understands what matters.

342
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,639
Here.

343
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:31,399
Zhenzhen.

344
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:32,840
What do you think of my painting?

345
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,919
It does look nice,

346
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,039
but didn't you draw me a bit too thin?

347
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:40,360
Did I?

348
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:44,639
Hey.

349
00:14:44,639 --> 00:14:45,440
Qi Zhi.

350
00:14:45,799 --> 00:14:47,039
You're back already?

351
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:47,960
Mission accomplished.

352
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,559
In a couple of days,

353
00:14:48,559 --> 00:14:49,360
we can head back to the capital.

354
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,159
Are you sure?

355
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,559
He is Prince Yu, after all.

356
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,919
What about Prince Yu?

357
00:14:53,399 --> 00:14:55,200
I clearly remember

358
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,840
that Prince Yu despises the palace.

359
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,440
Sure, he was reluctant,

360
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,080
but he understood what was at stake.

361
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:01,799
Get it?

362
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,639
I also think

363
00:15:03,639 --> 00:15:04,840
that this Prince Yu

364
00:15:04,879 --> 00:15:06,000
seems a little off.

365
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,840
Right? Right?

366
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,240
Extra! Extra!

367
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:11,120
Prince Yu's farewell tomorrow in the south!

368
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,039
Take a look.

369
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,000
Please have a look.

370
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:14,799
Extra! Extra!

371
00:15:15,039 --> 00:15:17,440
Prince Yu's farewell tomorrow in the south!

372
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,759
Wow.

373
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:20,840
News travels fast.

374
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,639
This is hardly reluctance.

375
00:15:24,399 --> 00:15:25,799
He can't wait to leave!

376
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:28,840
I told you something was off about him.

377
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,000
Boss

378
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,000
The window seats on the second floor,

379
00:15:45,039 --> 00:15:45,919
any left?

380
00:15:45,919 --> 00:15:46,639
Oh

381
00:15:46,639 --> 00:15:48,440
Prime spots have been booked out for ages.

382
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,840
Let's go.

383
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,000
Hey

384
00:15:54,639 --> 00:15:55,440
Waiter

385
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,639
Take these guests upstairs, quick!

386
00:15:57,639 --> 00:15:58,159
Hurry up!

387
00:15:58,159 --> 00:15:58,600
Zhenzhen,

388
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:01,000
you really are loaded.

389
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:01,559
Hey

390
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:02,000
Not really.

391
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,519
Just a little money for convenience.

392
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,159
As fellow artists,

393
00:16:06,159 --> 00:16:07,559
why is the gap between us so huge?

394
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:11,919
Because poverty limits your imagination.

395
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:18,240
Prince Yu, we'll miss you!

396
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,120
I know you all hate to see me go,

397
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:24,039
but as a prince,

398
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,720
the realm must come first.

399
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,360
What did I tell you?

400
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:30,600
Believe me now?

401
00:16:31,559 --> 00:16:33,360
Who knew Prince Yu would grow up

402
00:16:33,799 --> 00:16:35,320
to be so noble-minded.

403
00:16:36,519 --> 00:16:37,519
I wouldn't say so.

404
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:38,559
I agree.

405
00:16:38,559 --> 00:16:39,000
Prince Yu,

406
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:39,840
we'll miss you!

407
00:16:46,519 --> 00:16:47,639
Why did you lie to me?

408
00:16:48,639 --> 00:16:50,399
Last night you said you wouldn't leave,

409
00:16:50,399 --> 00:16:51,519
and that you'd marry me.

410
00:16:52,879 --> 00:16:53,440
Absurd!

411
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:55,440
I've never even met you, miss.

412
00:16:55,559 --> 00:16:56,799
Why would you say such a thing?

413
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,600
If you become emperor,

414
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,200
what's to become of me?

415
00:17:01,039 --> 00:17:01,840
Miss,

416
00:17:02,399 --> 00:17:03,720
I truly don't know you.

417
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,319
Please compose yourself.

418
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:07,160
Dying to be Princess Yu, are you?

419
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:11,640
Yun Xi

420
00:17:12,519 --> 00:17:13,319
Yun Xi

421
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:14,440
Yun...

422
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:15,599
Hey

423
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:17,039
Where are you going?

424
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:18,160
What "Xi" did he say?

425
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:19,960
Yun Xi

426
00:17:22,519 --> 00:17:23,200
Yun Xi

427
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:26,799
It really is you.

428
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,279
Hey!

429
00:17:28,279 --> 00:17:29,359
You two,

430
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,559
what's going on here?

431
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,640
So you're saying

432
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:40,839
Prince Yu came to see you every night

433
00:17:41,559 --> 00:17:42,960
and promised to marry you?

434
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,519
Impossible.

435
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:46,839
Didn't Prince Yu say

436
00:17:46,839 --> 00:17:48,759
he never goes out at night

437
00:17:48,759 --> 00:17:49,839
and doesn't see anyone?

438
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:51,319
I'm not lying to you.

439
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,480
Just last night he told me

440
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,720
he didn't want to be emperor.

441
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:57,720
If that's really the case,

442
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,160
then why did he pretend not to know you today?

443
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,200
I don't know either.

444
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,920
Why did he lie to me?

445
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:11,839
Uh...

446
00:18:11,839 --> 00:18:12,000
You...

447
00:18:12,839 --> 00:18:13,720
Don't be like that.

448
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:15,119
That's no way to talk to a lady.

449
00:18:15,559 --> 00:18:16,359
I...

450
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:17,960
I'm sorry.

451
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:19,319
Don't be sad.

452
00:18:19,519 --> 00:18:20,599
I believe you.

453
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:30,000
Now you think there's something off about him?

454
00:18:30,839 --> 00:18:33,039
I told you several times before and you didn't believe me.

455
00:18:33,039 --> 00:18:34,960
Your first love says one word and you believe her.

456
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:37,119
I saw him in Yun Xi's memories.

457
00:18:37,119 --> 00:18:37,960
She's not my first love.

458
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,240
She...

459
00:18:38,839 --> 00:18:40,759
is just my childhood sweetheart.

460
00:18:40,759 --> 00:18:41,640
So what if you saw him?

461
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:44,559
Prince Yu is in every girl's memory here.

462
00:18:44,559 --> 00:18:45,720
What does that prove?

463
00:18:45,839 --> 00:18:47,640
Why are you being so unreasonable?

464
00:18:48,039 --> 00:18:49,319
Yun Xi and I have been childhood friends.

465
00:18:49,319 --> 00:18:51,440
She'd never joke about her reputation.

466
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:51,720
Right.

467
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,960
I'm just being unreasonable.

468
00:18:53,039 --> 00:18:53,640
Don't follow me.

469
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,000
Hey!

470
00:18:54,599 --> 00:18:54,960
Hey!

471
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,440
Don't touch me.

472
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,839
You're not jealous, are you?

473
00:18:58,039 --> 00:18:58,839
Jealous?

474
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:05,240
I just think we don't have any evidence.

475
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:07,759
Getting evidence is easy.

476
00:19:07,759 --> 00:19:08,720
We'll have it tonight.

477
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:10,799
What do you mean?

478
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:12,960
Didn't Yun Xi say

479
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,440
Prince Yu goes to the tavern to see her every night?

480
00:19:18,319 --> 00:19:19,000
You mean...

481
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,640
follow him?

482
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,240
Mm-hmm.

483
00:19:34,319 --> 00:19:36,519
Are you sure Prince Yu will come out from here?

484
00:19:36,599 --> 00:19:38,240
Remember the Caped Man?

485
00:19:38,799 --> 00:19:40,599
I told you something was off about him.

486
00:19:40,599 --> 00:19:41,599
You wouldn't believe me.

487
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,319
What are you doing here?

488
00:20:04,599 --> 00:20:05,440
What's wrong?

489
00:20:06,599 --> 00:20:07,640
I can't believe he's such a scoundrel.

490
00:20:10,839 --> 00:20:12,240
Let me explain it to you slowly.

491
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:14,759
I'm going to teach him a lesson!

492
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,880
Why are you butting into someone else's business?

493
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,039
Wait!

494
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:30,319
Princess.

495
00:20:30,319 --> 00:20:32,240
Are you comfortable here?

496
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:33,200
No.

497
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,200
This manor is shabby.

498
00:20:36,839 --> 00:20:38,000
My apologies, Princess.

499
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,839
Do you actually have business or not?

500
00:20:45,839 --> 00:20:46,359
No business.

501
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:48,839
Can't I just come to see you?

502
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,799
What's gotten into you this early?

503
00:20:52,759 --> 00:20:53,559
Princess.

504
00:20:54,319 --> 00:20:56,319
You and I will marry sooner or later.

505
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:58,000
Since that's the case,

506
00:21:01,599 --> 00:21:02,359
how about

507
00:21:02,359 --> 00:21:04,559
you give in to me right now?

508
00:21:09,519 --> 00:21:10,319
Ha.

509
00:21:12,519 --> 00:21:14,720
I think you're tired of living.

510
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,640
Give in to you?

511
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,599
Today I'll show you

512
00:21:22,599 --> 00:21:23,519
how scumbags end up.

513
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,440
Hey, hey!

514
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:26,759
Let go!

515
00:21:27,599 --> 00:21:29,119
Thank you, lady, for letting me out.

516
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:32,119
Don't tell me

517
00:21:32,119 --> 00:21:34,200
I knocked you senseless.

518
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:41,240
I haven't seen the sun in so long.

519
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,240
Huh?

520
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:44,880
Really?

521
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,440
I knocked him senseless.

522
00:21:48,839 --> 00:21:49,720
Qi Zhi!

523
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,559
Qi Zhi!

524
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,240
Qi Zhi!

525
00:21:53,799 --> 00:21:55,599
So you're saying you have two personalities.

526
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:56,640
Mm.

527
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:57,720
One in the daytime,

528
00:21:57,799 --> 00:21:58,599
one at night.

529
00:21:58,839 --> 00:21:59,599
Mm.

530
00:21:59,839 --> 00:22:00,440
The you right now

531
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:01,960
is the one who likes Yun Xi.

532
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:02,799
Mm.

533
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:04,519
Could you say something besides nodding?

534
00:22:06,839 --> 00:22:08,359
I've hated the palace since childhood.

535
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,400
And hated reading.

536
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:12,000
But Mother said I had a talent for ruling.

537
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:13,799
She always wanted me to be emperor.

538
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,839
I didn't want to defy my mother,

539
00:22:16,359 --> 00:22:17,200
nor did I want to betray my own

540
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,200
true intentions.

541
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:19,440
So...

542
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,519
So you gradually

543
00:22:23,519 --> 00:22:26,240
created a persona to meet her demands,

544
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:29,240
while letting you escape reality.

545
00:22:31,359 --> 00:22:32,440
He's so professional.

546
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:35,200
No wonder Yun Xi and the Crown Prince found him off.

547
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:38,359
You mean

548
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:40,000
I accidentally

549
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:42,160
pulled you out?

550
00:22:43,519 --> 00:22:44,319
That's right.

551
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,440
His scheming against you

552
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:49,440
was to make me give up completely,

553
00:22:49,519 --> 00:22:50,920
so he could smoothly take the throne.

554
00:22:51,799 --> 00:22:52,599
Shameless!

555
00:22:53,759 --> 00:22:54,559
Shameless!

556
00:22:56,839 --> 00:22:57,599
But

557
00:22:58,359 --> 00:23:00,640
my time out is getting shorter lately.

558
00:23:01,799 --> 00:23:02,680
I'm afraid that one day

559
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:04,839
I'll disappear.

560
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,839
Why don't you tell

561
00:23:07,839 --> 00:23:08,559
Yun Xi about this?

562
00:23:08,559 --> 00:23:09,359
I...

563
00:23:11,599 --> 00:23:13,240
I'm afraid she'll think I'm a monster.

564
00:23:15,759 --> 00:23:16,799
Maybe disappearing would be

565
00:23:16,799 --> 00:23:18,960
a kind of relief for me.

566
00:23:20,839 --> 00:23:22,039
But I can't bear to leave Yun Xi alone in this world.

567
00:23:24,359 --> 00:23:25,000
So you're hoping

568
00:23:25,000 --> 00:23:26,799
we'll help you?

569
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:27,960
No problem.

570
00:23:29,319 --> 00:23:29,839
How about

571
00:23:29,839 --> 00:23:31,759
we just kill off that bad personality of yours?

572
00:23:33,359 --> 00:23:33,960
Kill him?

573
00:23:35,359 --> 00:23:36,440
Thank you, Princess.

574
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,839
Are you two out of your minds?

575
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:43,759
What's wrong?

576
00:23:44,359 --> 00:23:45,640
May I ask how exactly you plan to

577
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:46,759
kill that bad personality?

578
00:23:49,839 --> 00:23:50,319
I'll just...

579
00:23:50,319 --> 00:23:51,240
I'll just...

580
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:55,240
The moment that bad personality appears,

581
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:57,720
I'll just stab him.

582
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:00,599
Stab him?

583
00:24:01,759 --> 00:24:04,160
Wouldn't both personalities die then?

584
00:24:12,519 --> 00:24:13,319
Yu'er

585
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:16,200
It's time to return to your chambers

586
00:24:16,799 --> 00:24:17,599
Mother

587
00:24:22,799 --> 00:24:23,839
What are you all doing?

588
00:24:26,359 --> 00:24:27,440
We...

589
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:28,119
Oh

590
00:24:29,759 --> 00:24:30,440
The three of us were discussing

591
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,440
matters following Prince Yu's ascension

592
00:24:34,440 --> 00:24:36,319
Prince Yu is truly a great strategist

593
00:24:36,599 --> 00:24:37,559
learned and well-informed

594
00:24:38,759 --> 00:24:41,920
We've both benefited immensely

595
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:42,960
Hmm

596
00:24:43,599 --> 00:24:44,960
Naturally

597
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:46,599
Since the discussion is finished

598
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,759
then off you go

599
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,240
Yes

600
00:24:57,319 --> 00:24:58,440
Now I know why he never sees me during the day

601
00:25:01,319 --> 00:25:02,160
Because during the day

602
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:04,160
he doesn't remember me at all

603
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,039
He didn't tell you

604
00:25:06,359 --> 00:25:07,640
because he has his own struggles

605
00:25:08,119 --> 00:25:08,920
Yes

606
00:25:10,839 --> 00:25:13,039
Stop being angry about what happened that day

607
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:19,119
I'm not angry

608
00:25:20,799 --> 00:25:23,319
I'm thinking he must be in such pain now

609
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,400
and I can't help him

610
00:25:31,319 --> 00:25:31,680
No

611
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:33,039
I'm going to Prince Yu's manor

612
00:25:33,039 --> 00:25:35,519
Going there now

613
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:37,359
won't solve anything

614
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,200
I don't believe he doesn't remember me

615
00:25:39,559 --> 00:25:41,559
Seeing me, he's bound to remember something

616
00:25:42,119 --> 00:25:42,920
Sit down first

617
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:43,079
Sit down

618
00:25:43,079 --> 00:25:44,440
Let's think this through

619
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:44,920
Indeed

620
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:45,720
Sit

621
00:25:50,559 --> 00:25:51,599
I just want to help him

622
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,839
In the current situation

623
00:25:55,119 --> 00:25:55,839
not adding to his troubles

624
00:25:55,839 --> 00:25:57,440
is already helping him

625
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:58,839
Exactly

626
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:10,440
My lady

627
00:26:10,599 --> 00:26:10,920
Master

628
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,240
Yu'er's condition lately

629
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,160
hasn't been good

630
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:16,920
Is your medicine no longer working?

631
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:17,240
Hmm

632
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,000
Well

633
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:20,519
By all reason, this shouldn't happen

634
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:22,960
It must be that

635
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:25,160
something unusual triggered him

636
00:26:32,839 --> 00:26:35,440
Is there any way to fix it?

637
00:26:36,039 --> 00:26:36,960
It's no matter

638
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:38,519
I'll have Granny Soup

639
00:26:38,519 --> 00:26:39,240
adjust the medicine

640
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:40,440
and increase the dosage, that's all.

641
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:43,240
Mm

642
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,039
Guards

643
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:57,000
Stop right there

644
00:27:00,599 --> 00:27:01,519
Why are you running?

645
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,599
I...

646
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:07,839
I have other matters to attend to

647
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:08,599
Princess

648
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:09,640
Please

649
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:11,200
do as you wish

650
00:27:11,799 --> 00:27:12,599
Wait a moment

651
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:26,720
Hey

652
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:35,240
Yu'er

653
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:37,960
Yes

654
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:38,759
Mother

655
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:39,519
He's about

656
00:27:39,519 --> 00:27:40,359
to come out

657
00:27:40,599 --> 00:27:41,599
Take Yu'er away

658
00:27:41,599 --> 00:27:42,240
Yes, ma'am

659
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:48,200
Hey

660
00:27:50,079 --> 00:27:51,839
Am I really that scary?

661
00:27:53,599 --> 00:27:55,319
Compared to his mother,

662
00:27:55,759 --> 00:27:57,160
you fall a bit short

663
00:27:57,839 --> 00:27:59,680
Comparing me to her?

664
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:01,000
You want to die?

665
00:28:01,359 --> 00:28:02,359
Sorry, sorry

666
00:28:02,559 --> 00:28:04,119
I take back what I just said

667
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,319
You're scarier than her

668
00:28:06,319 --> 00:28:07,119
Hey

669
00:28:08,119 --> 00:28:09,359
Hey

670
00:28:09,359 --> 00:28:10,240
Now that you mention it,

671
00:28:10,599 --> 00:28:12,000
I actually feel sorry for him

672
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:14,359
Driven to this state by his own mother

673
00:28:16,319 --> 00:28:17,599
I really want to help him,

674
00:28:17,839 --> 00:28:19,519
but I don't know where to start

675
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:21,599
Don't worry

676
00:28:21,599 --> 00:28:23,119
We'll figure something out

677
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,000
It's fine

678
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,000
Worst case,

679
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,160
every time I see him,

680
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:29,240
I'll beat him up

681
00:28:29,519 --> 00:28:30,839
I'll make sure he's himself again

682
00:28:31,599 --> 00:28:33,240
That's only temporary

683
00:28:33,599 --> 00:28:35,640
You can't wake someone pretending to sleep

684
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:38,440
Unless he's willing to wake up himself

685
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:40,720
Anyway, if anyone needs help,

686
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:41,640
just let me know

687
00:28:42,599 --> 00:28:44,000
Hmm, besides being rich,

688
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:45,240
I can't really help with anything else

689
00:28:45,839 --> 00:28:46,759
It's fine, Zhenzhen

690
00:28:46,839 --> 00:28:48,000
Of all the rich people I've met,

691
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:49,640
you're the cutest

692
00:28:50,079 --> 00:28:50,759
Pfft

693
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,000
If everyone's fine,

694
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,599
let's go check on Yun Xi

695
00:28:56,599 --> 00:28:57,440
Leaving her alone at the tavern,

696
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:59,359
I just don't feel at ease
